data.text: @VSGeminixx @RMaclean58 Again, not bothered. Humorous AF!!!!!
@RMaclean58 @sabri930 I don't care what other people think. And seeing how much it bothered you, I'm doing it again soon.
@VSGeminixx I looked at DJ's account and saw mostly stuff about her. But I have muted all the 50 Shades crazies so maybe that's the answer to the problem. JD's account looking a lot clearer too.

@VSGeminixx @sabri930 Perhaps do it when your fav isn’t actually promoting a project. With what she has coming up one would think as a fan you would of spent more than 6 tweets promoting it as opposed to talking about unjust hashtags. #JamieDornan ✌️
@RMaclean58 @Millieinbandw @sabri930 You realize you're making my day, do you? Please continue.
@sabri930 @Millieinbandw @RMaclean58 @sararivae I love making people laugh.

@VSGeminixx Those two trolls are the same person talking to themselves and had their accounts suspended 10 times. They didn’t even start talking about their ‘famous’ idol until after fifty shades, but OK whatever they say. 😹

@VSGeminixx @sabri930 @RMaclean58 @sararivae Yep but sadly that won’t stop them to tag our favs to post that have nothing to do with them. Someday they will move on 🤞🏻

@Millieinbandw @sabri930 @RMaclean58 @sararivae I know, that's why I decided to annoy people back. It's working. If I'm annoyed, then everybody else will be annoyed. My pettiness knows no bounds.

@VSGeminixx Well,I was on IG...
I guess I have to use the same logic as yours 😉

@VSGeminixx @sabri930 Refer to my other tweet I put Jamie Dornan in my timeline and you popped up. That’s how twitter and tags work. So your fav has so much to promote and you’re still hung up on Jamie. Don’t blame you. 😘
@Millieinbandw @sabri930 @RMaclean58 @sararivae There is and people need to learn how to properly use tags. It is annoying and won't be tolerated.

@RMaclean58 @sabri930 Sorry, I don't remember specifically talking about you, since I don't know you. Can you refresh my memory and post the tweet where I tagged you? Thanks. And last I checked I run this account.

@sabri930 @RMaclean58 @VSGeminixx @sararivae You will find Dakota’s pictures under Amelia Warner hashtag. 🤷🏻‍♀️ People use their hashtags to get more views and likes, simple as that. I don’t understand it but there is no harm (unless they use them to insult) There is no need to attack anyone because they use a hashtag.

@sabri930 @VSGeminixx @sararivae Meanwhile I put jamies tag on twitter and that’s how I saw her tweet. 🤦🏻‍♀️
